{"tid":655403,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人成日孤立自己？","createTime":"2018-05-06T13:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T14:46:22.000Z","uid":64259,"like":112,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"02af7ec8f544bcb1490c5b8b6d24aa6d0d6dab87","tid":655403,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"呢個世界 真係唔會有人明自己<br />\n我唔想同人溝通<br />\n因為佢地講野無營養<br />\n一係日日睇靚仔<br />\n一係話啱啱條女好正<br />\n<br />\n講人生大道理<br />\nd人諗少少就得出結論<br />\n諗野太唔全面了<br />\n<br />\n慢慢 我覺得 溝通都係無用<br />\n唔同世界 唔應該勉強<br />\n所以 我就無交到心既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔鐘意附和<br />\n注定一支公 咁就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99e46035742c3a4970b85ecb1fec4b83aef90f9","tid":655403,"uid":78971,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"我冇你咁多諗法<br />\n純粹唔想同太多人接觸<br />\n覺得要管理好啲關係好煩"},{"pid":"d54a38cec3722abb5f567f3004096f550c8a3b08","tid":655403,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edbbd1a82d2604da2ee4449a262a1bce05f5b1b0","tid":655403,"uid":37713,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"中二病<br />\n<br />\n利申同你幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ea8d21fab6ecb2002054594c0a907a0205a566","tid":655403,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:05:57.000Z","msg":"似係你個生活圈子問題多啲"},{"pid":"11fd023577b80d54bdb9687d483f90fea31b8d69","tid":655403,"uid":71433,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"edbbd1a82d2604da2ee4449a262a1bce05f5b1b0","tid":655403,"uid":37713,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"中二病<br />\n<br />\n利申同你幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"覺得自己自命不凡<img src=\"/a